[
  {
    "id": "dlg_0001",
    "speaker": "char_tu_er_ye",
    "speaker_name": "屠二爷",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "快，快去找大夫来！",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0003",
    "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
    "speaker_name": "老张",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "现在小店的张还没有开，可是包子、馒头、卤菜都是现成的，客官你想吃什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0004",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我想吃你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0005",
    "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
    "speaker_name": "老张",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你要吃我？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0006",
    "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
    "speaker_name": "老张",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你为什么要吃我？我有什么好吃的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0007",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你当然好吃。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0008",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "如果我不吃你，我怎么能活到现在？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0009",
    "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
    "speaker_name": "老张",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "原来是你，你这个小坏蛋！",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0011",
    "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
    "speaker_name": "老张",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你要报答我，你以前就说过你要一百倍一千倍来报答我。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 91,
    "line_end": 91
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0012",
    "speaker": "char_lao_zhang",
    "speaker_name": "老张",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那时候我就相信你总有一天会做到的，可是我现在反而有点不相信了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 2,
    "line_start": 91,
    "line_end": 91
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0014",
    "speaker": "char_fang_tian_hao",
    "speaker_name": "方大老板",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "人家赤手空拳不到几年就挣到了上亿万的身价，你们比得上吗？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0016",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李先生你贵姓？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 161,
    "line_end": 161
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0017",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李先生当然是姓李的，",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 163,
    "line_end": 163
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0018",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可是韩先生呢？韩先生你贵姓？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 163,
    "line_end": 163
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0019",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不错，在下正是实授正六品御前带刀护卫，领刑部正捕缺，少林南宗俗家弟子，蒲田韩峻。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 175,
    "line_end": 175
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0020",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你难道是来找我的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 185,
    "line_end": 185
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0021",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你就是李坏？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 187,
    "line_end": 187
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0023",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "从张家口到这里你一共走了多少天？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 191,
    "line_end": 191
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0024",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我不知道，",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 193,
    "line_end": 193
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0025",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我没有算过。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 3,
    "line_start": 193,
    "line_end": 193
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0027",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李坏，你这个小王八蛋，真的是坏死了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0028",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你倒真的是逍遥自在。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0029",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你知不知道韩峻和我爸爸找来了那批人，为了要抓你，几乎已经把城里每一寸地都翻过来了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0030",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我知道，我当然知道。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0031",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可是我一点都不担心。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0032",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "因为他们都认为城里最恨我的人就是你，而且你又是你爸爸的女儿，如果他们会找到这里来，他们简直就不是人，是活鬼了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 67,
    "line_end": 67
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0033",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我知道你想不到的，就连我自己都想不到。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0034",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们都以为今生今世再也看不到阁下这张脸了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0035",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那个小姑娘呢？那个从月亮掉下来的漂漂亮亮的，神神秘秘的，专门喜欢杀人的小姑娘呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 79,
    "line_end": 79
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0036",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "她今天也没有来。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 79,
    "line_end": 79
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0037",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "其实我也知道她不会来的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 4,
    "line_start": 83,
    "line_end": 83
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0038",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可可、可可、可可、可可……",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 115,
    "line_end": 115
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0040",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "她是不是还活着？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 125,
    "line_end": 125
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0041",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可可，我就是李坏，我就是那个坏死了的坏小鬼，我已经坏得连我自己　都快要被我自己气死了。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 161,
    "line_end": 161
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0042",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "像我这么坏的人，已经坏得再也找不出　第二个了，所以我相信你一定还认得我。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 161,
    "line_end": 161
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0044",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这里怎么变成这个样子呢？这里的那些人呢？这究竟是怎么回事？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 105,
    "line_end": 105
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0045",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李坏，你这坏小鬼，你真的坏死了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 147,
    "line_end": 147
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0046",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你还认得我，我知道你一定还认得我，否则你就不会打我。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 173,
    "line_end": 173
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0047",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我认得你？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 175,
    "line_end": 175
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0048",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我认得你吗？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 5,
    "line_start": 175,
    "line_end": 175
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0050",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "放你妈的狗臭屁，",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0051",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你这个乌龟王八蛋，你偷了金子，要我来替你背黑锅，我也可以原谅你的；因为如果我是你，我说不定也会这么做的，可是你为什么一定还要我的命？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0052",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "因为你坏。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0053",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "像你这么坏的人，如果不死，往后的日子我怎么能睡得着觉。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0054",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你知道你的女儿肚子里已经有我的孩子了？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 53,
    "line_end": 53
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0055",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你打我没关系，只可惜你永远打不到你女儿肚子里的孩子。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0056",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "她这么样恨我，这么样害我，就因为她肚子里有了我的孩子，而我却硬是不理她。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0057",
    "speaker": "char_fang_tian_hao",
    "speaker_name": "方天豪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大总管，几乎已经有十年未履江湖了，今天怎么会忽然光临此地？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 113
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0058",
    "speaker": "char_fang_tian_hao",
    "speaker_name": "方天豪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老庄主最近身子可安泰？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 115,
    "line_end": 115
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0059",
    "speaker": "char_fang_tian_hao",
    "speaker_name": "方天豪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "少庄主的病最近有没有好一点？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 115,
    "line_end": 115
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0060",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "老庄主的身子一天比一天的坏，小庄主已经病得快死了，你们问他，他能说什么？他当然连一个屁都不会放。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 119,
    "line_end": 119
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0061",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大胆，无礼。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 121,
    "line_end": 121
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0062",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "大年初一，你不在家里，陪着孩子过年，跑到这里来瞪着我看什么？我有什么好看的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 35,
    "line_end": 35
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0063",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你姓什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 39,
    "line_end": 39
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0064",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你不知道？原来你连自己姓什么都不知道。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0065",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "为什么一定要知道？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0066",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我没有爹没有娘没有姓，那是我家的事，跟你有什么狗屁关系，你凭什么问我？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0067",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你怎么知道跟我没关系？我到这里来，就是特地来找你的。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0068",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "找我？你又不认得我找我干吗？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 51,
    "line_end": 51
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0069",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我认得你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 53,
    "line_end": 53
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0070",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你认得我？你怎么会认得我？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0071",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你知道我是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0072",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我也认得你的父亲，如果没有他，现在我就算活着没死也比你更惨。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 7,
    "line_start": 57,
    "line_end": 57
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0074",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你要带我到哪里去？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0075",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "带你回家去。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 7,
    "line_end": 7
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0076",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "回家？我哪里有家？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0078",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我相信你一定会以你的家为荣，你的家也一定会以你为荣。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0079",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "以我为荣？像我这么样一个已经从头顶坏到脚底坏透子的坏小孩？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0081",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我还不坏？怎么样才算坏？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0082",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "能做得出那种卑鄙无耻下流的事的人才算坏。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0083",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可是你做不出。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0084",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你怎么知道我做不出？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0085",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "因为你是李家的人，是李家的骨血。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 8,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0086",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好，我请你喝酒。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0087",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我一定让你痛痛快快地喝一顿。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0088",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那么你就醉吧！",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 47,
    "line_end": 47
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0089",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们不是朋友，可是今天晚上我可以陪你醉一场。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 47,
    "line_end": 47
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0090",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们为什么不是朋友？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0091",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "一定要记住，你是李家的二少爷，以你现在的身份和地位，天下已经没有一个人配做你的朋友。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 53,
    "line_end": 53
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0092",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "没事，喝酒。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0093",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那个人真是个绝世无双的美人，我保证你看见他也会心动的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 113
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0094",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我保证只要还是个男人的男人，看见他都会心动的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 113
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0095",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你呢？你的心有没有动？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 9,
    "line_start": 115,
    "line_end": 115
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0098",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "谢谢，你对我们的夸赞，我们一定会永远牢记在心。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 27,
    "line_end": 27
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0099",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "在下说的只不过是实情而已。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0100",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那么我也可以向阁下保证，阁下说的一点都没有错。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0101",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我可以保证李坏先生在今晨日出之前绝不会死。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 31,
    "line_end": 31
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0103",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "太夫人说的话，在下绝对相信。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0104",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这位女士真的就是公孙太夫人？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 41,
    "line_end": 41
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0105",
    "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
    "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "可是她看起来实在不像，太夫人的年纪怎么会这么轻？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0106",
    "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
    "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "太夫人说出来的话怎么会这么样不负责任？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0107",
    "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
    "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你说我年轻，我实在不敢当。你说我不负责任，我也承担不起。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0108",
    "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
    "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "让人看不懂的招式，总是让人不能不佩服的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 91,
    "line_end": 91
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0109",
    "speaker": "char_zi_teng_hua",
    "speaker_name": "紫藤花",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "所以等太夫人魂归九天之后，每年今天我一定以香花祭酒，来纪念太夫人的忌辰。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 10,
    "line_start": 91,
    "line_end": 91
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0110",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你出手，并不是为了求胜，只不过为了要找一个值得你出手的对象而已。成败胜负根本就没有放在你的心上。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0111",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "如果不配让你出手的人，就算跪在地上求你，你也不会对他伸出一根手指。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 15,
    "line_end": 15
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0112",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我就知道你会明白的，如果你不明白，世上还有谁能明白？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0113",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "如果我不败，这世上还有谁败？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 19,
    "line_end": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0114",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我非常感谢，你愿意把我当做你第五个对手，我实在觉得非常荣幸。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0115",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那也是没法子的事。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0116",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我已经收了别人三万两黄金来换你一条命。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 45,
    "line_end": 45
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0117",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们夫妻一直都很守信约的，只要约一订，无论在什么情况下，我们都会守约的。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 51,
    "line_end": 51
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0118",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我从本不拍别人的马屁，可是今天我们就算是生死之敌，就算我在顷刻之间就会死在你手里，或者我在顷刻之间就会杀了你。我也要先说一句话。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0119",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公孙先生，你虽然永败无胜，可是你虽败犹荣，我佩服你。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 29,
    "line_end": 29
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0120",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我真想不到，我的命居然有这么值钱。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 49,
    "line_end": 49
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0121",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我也是个很有原则的人，而且我现在还不想死，所以我虽然很佩服你，我还是决心要让你再败一次。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 11,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0122",
    "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
    "speaker_name": "李曼青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小李飞刀昔日的雄风，很可能已经不会在任何人身上出现。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 37,
    "line_end": 37
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0123",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你不能走，现在你绝不能走。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 71,
    "line_end": 71
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0124",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我知道你现在心里在想什么，可是你也应该知道你的父亲现在是多么的需要你，不管怎么样，你总是他亲生的骨肉，是他血中的血，骨中的骨。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 71,
    "line_end": 71
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0125",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你更要知道，要想重振李家的威风，只有靠你了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 75,
    "line_end": 75
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0126",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你知不知道你的父亲这次为什么一定要我找你来？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 89,
    "line_end": 89
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0127",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我只知道，不管他要我去做什么事我都会去做的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 93,
    "line_end": 93
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0128",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "今天我找你来，并不是为了要对你解释这件事，这件事也是永远无法解释的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 181,
    "line_end": 181
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0129",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "多年前，我初出道急着要表现自己，为了要证明我的声名，并不是靠我祖先的余荫而得来的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 191,
    "line_end": 191
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0130",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那时候，武林中有一位非常成功的人，战无不胜，几乎横扫了武林。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 191,
    "line_end": 191
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0131",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我一战而胜举世无双的名剑，当然欣喜若狂。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 201,
    "line_end": 201
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0132",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "付出代价。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 253,
    "line_end": 253
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0133",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "无论谁做错事之后，都要付出代价。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 12,
    "line_start": 253,
    "line_end": 253
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0134",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你是不是姓李，是不是叫李坏？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 43,
    "line_end": 43
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0135",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你的意思是说，你和内库的那件盗案完全没有关系？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 55,
    "line_end": 55
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0136",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "是的，我和那件案子完全无关。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 57,
    "line_end": 57
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0137",
    "speaker": "char_han_jun",
    "speaker_name": "韩峻",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那么你这几个月来所挥霍花去的钱财，是从哪里来的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 59,
    "line_end": 59
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0138",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李坏，没有关系的。不管韩总捕问你什么，你都不妨大胆照实说。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 73,
    "line_end": 73
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0139",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "只要你说的是实话，我们一定会给你一个公道。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 73,
    "line_end": 73
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0140",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "韩总捕，你再问。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 79,
    "line_end": 79
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0141",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我相信他不会不说实话的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 79,
    "line_end": 79
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0142",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这些日子来，我相信你父亲教给你很多关于飞刀的秘法。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 113
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0143",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "再加上这个册子里的要诀和你自己的苦练，我相信你一定可以练成你们李家的飞刀，因为你本来就是李家的人，你的血里面本来就有你们李家的血。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 113,
    "line_end": 113
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0144",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这个锦囊里有什么？就没有人知道了。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 117,
    "line_end": 117
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0145",
    "speaker": "char_tie_yin_yi",
    "speaker_name": "铁银衣",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "因为这个锦囊是你母亲要你父亲交给你的，我们谁也没有打开来看过。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 13,
    "line_start": 117,
    "line_end": 117
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0146",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "今天已经是正月初六了，是接财神的日子。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 77,
    "line_end": 77
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0147",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "今天晚上家家户户都在接财神，我们呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 77,
    "line_end": 77
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0148",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我们要接的不是财神。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 79,
    "line_end": 79
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0149",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不是财神，是什么神？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 81,
    "line_end": 81
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0150",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "是不是月神？是不是那位刀如月光的月神？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 81,
    "line_end": 81
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0151",
    "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
    "speaker_name": "月神",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不错，我是想接月神。因为在某一些古老的传说中，月的意思就是死。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 85,
    "line_end": 85
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0152",
    "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
    "speaker_name": "月神",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "太阳是生，月是死。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 85,
    "line_end": 85
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0154",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "弟弟已经睡着了，睡得很好，所以我才进来看看小姐。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 61,
    "line_end": 61
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0156",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你看我干什么？我有什么好看的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 63,
    "line_end": 63
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0157",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小姐，我知道你一直都有心事，可是这几个月来你的心事又比以前更重得多了，你为什么要这样子呢？为什么要这么样折磨自己？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 14,
    "line_start": 65,
    "line_end": 65
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0158",
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "寂寞真是一种享受。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 15,
    "line_start": 25,
    "line_end": 25
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0159",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小姐，正月十五那天，我一定也要陪你过去。因为我要看看那个李曼青究竟是个什么样的人，当年为什么要把老爹逼得那么惨。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0160",
    "speaker": "char_xiao_xing",
    "speaker_name": "小星",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我娘告诉我这件事的时候，我就一直在盼望着有一天能亲眼看到这个李曼青死在小姐你的刀下。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 5,
    "line_end": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0161",
    "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
    "speaker_name": "李曼青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "李曼青不会死在我刀下的。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0162",
    "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
    "speaker_name": "李曼青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "因为正月十五那天，他根本不会应战。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 9,
    "line_end": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0163",
    "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
    "speaker_name": "李曼青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "难道李曼青是个贪生怕死的人？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 11,
    "line_end": 11
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0164",
    "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
    "speaker_name": "李曼青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他不怕死，可是他怕败。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0165",
    "speaker": "char_li_man_qing",
    "speaker_name": "李曼青",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他是小李探花的后代，他不能败。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 13,
    "line_end": 13
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0166",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "小姐，李坏李少爷难道真的是他们李家的后代？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 17,
    "line_end": 17
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0168",
    "speaker": "char_li_huai",
    "speaker_name": "李坏",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "那么他一定不知道向李家挑战的人就是你？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 21,
    "line_end": 21
  },
  {
    "id": "dlg_0170",
    "speaker": "char_yue_shen",
    "speaker_name": "月神",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "他是个绝顶聪明的人，现在他一定已经知道了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 16,
    "line_start": 23,
    "line_end": 23
  }
]